sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant DSW
    participant Vault
    participant KDC
    User->>DSW: Login (LDAP)
    DSW->>Vault: Store encrypted credential
    DSW-->>User: Login success
    User->>DSW: Create notebook
    DSW->>Vault: Retrieve & decrypt credential
    DSW->>KDC: kinit (obtain ticket)
    KDC-->>DSW: Ticket
    loop Ticket monitoring
        DSW->>KDC: Check expiry
        alt Expiring soon
            DSW->>Vault: Get credential
            DSW->>KDC: Renew ticket
        end
    end
    DSW-->>User: Access data lake